information: Dried fruits and nuts are our business! hpm Warenhandelsagentur was founded in 1990. We have been supplying European customers with dried fruits and nuts from producers all around the world for a quarter of a century. This means we bring supply and demand together and supply the processing industry, much like importers and wholesalers. Our operations are straightforward and efficient. Our core expertise lies in the variety and quality of our long-standing contacts with suppliers, retailers and producers around the world. Our offer goes far above and beyond typical intermediary activity. These days, we primarily see ourselves as a service provider with a diverse portfolio of services. Consequently, we have become an important trade link between the source of our products and Europe.
